Dialogue: 2,0:00:01.15,0:00:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... breaking up?
Dialogue: 2,0:00:03.86,0:00:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you failed at the hula-hoop?
Comment: 2,0:01:48.54,0:01:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:01:50.54,0:01:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't make it over\Nthe wall that I am to myself.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So the only thing to do is to break up.
Dialogue: 2,0:01:56.79,0:02:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were only three\Naway from your 200 target!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you round up, that was 200!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Round up... shisha gonyu...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:06.51,0:02:08.60,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– So many boobs...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.93,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Did... did you say "boobs"?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.60,0:02:12.35,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– So many boobs... So many boobs...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:08.93,0:02:12.35,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– I bet Kanade's picturing something else entirely.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:15.90,0:02:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to break up.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.15,0:02:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when I've just reaffirmed that I do love you.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:27.74,0:02:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:29.70,0:02:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade... don't you get one last chance?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:33.37,0:02:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One last chance?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:35.17,0:02:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cool to be hard on yourself and all,
Dialogue: 2,0:02:38.63,0:02:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but isn't a never-give-up spirit\Nwhat makes a {\i1}real{\i0} man?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:42.67,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point...
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.63,0:02:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho, will you give me one last chance?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.97,0:02:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 2,0:02:53.10,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... we'll throw triplefin for it.
Dialogue: 2,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Triplefin?
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, whoever wins three rounds of\Nrock-paper-scissors is the winner.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You say "Triplefin!" as you throw.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Kaho... let's do this!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:07.62,0:03:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What, with {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:09.20,0:03:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, and...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Triplefin! Triplefin!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Triplefin!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:21.21,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaho... you're good at this.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:24.51,0:03:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I have to go and win three in a row?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:30.18,0:03:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is fate.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.56,0:03:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:36.81,0:03:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Poof.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade...
Dialogue: 2,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Nikaidou!
Dialogue: 2,0:03:49.79,0:03:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the face?
Dialogue: 2,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you like Kaho, you\Nshould be glad they broke up.
Dialogue: 2,0:03:57.08,0:03:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why'd you even mention\Nthat "one last chance" stuff?
Dialogue: 2,0:04:00.79,0:04:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I just... I don't want to see\Nthe person I like looking sad...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:09.05,0:04:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in a sense,
Dialogue: 2,0:04:10.76,0:04:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you {\i1}did{\i0} finish them off\Nin the lousiest way possible.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:22.40,0:04:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment we met...\Nthough I didn't know why...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.11,0:04:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was attracted to him...\Nhe made my heart pound...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.41,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon Kanade was all I could think about.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.91,0:04:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dating or broken up:
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.61,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt words like that will\Nchange my relationship with him.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:42.34,0:04:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure my beloved Kanade\Nwill still be there tomorrow.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:47.31,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to be his girlfriend right now.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:50.68,0:04:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't love at the same speed...\NI'll wait till we can.
Dialogue: 2,0:04:57.27,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Come tomorrow, I know Kanade will be the same.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Brrrm! Boosh! Screee!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morninja!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Here: the Kanade Times!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.32,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Good boy.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.76,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– He's the same old Kanade, all right!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:12.32,0:05:13.76,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Okay, so gimme your seaweed!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:05:18.21,0:05:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:21.78,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need breakfast today...
Dialogue: 2,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ignore her?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We broke up.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:33.65,0:05:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the type to be friends with my exes.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.19,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– You have never dated\Nbefore—how can you be a "type"?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.55,0:05:42.05,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Looks like he's seen some\Nless-than-wholesome TV shows.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.05,0:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you break up, not being nice\Nis best for both of you.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:45.52,0:05:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did your mom tell you that?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You just do whatever she says, don't you.
Dialogue: 2,0:05:52.57,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You love your mother?\NLike, an Oedipus complex?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you mad?
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.69,0:06:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids get mad when you tell them\Nthey have an Oedipus complex.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.14,0:06:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with loving\Nthe person who gave birth to you.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:09.07,0:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't do whatever she says.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:11.73,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trusting the words\Nof someone I love and trust.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:18.65,0:06:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very true.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.55,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wrong. Sorry.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,'S okay.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be lonely, not being able to see your mom.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lonely. Everyone's here with me.
Dialogue: 2,0:06:33.39,0:06:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:39.45,0:06:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you Namiko's upbeat riding style!
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.34,0:06:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The demanding game of diving\Nthrough a hula-hoop you have thrown
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,requires the leg strength\Nto run alongside the hoop
Dialogue: 2,0:06:55.13,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and a high level of balance,\Nplus flexibility and decisiveness,
Dialogue: 2,0:06:59.89,0:07:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when jumping through it.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Records tell of five princes\Nin ancient Greece playing this game
Dialogue: 2,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,to determine who would take the throne,
Dialogue: 2,0:07:07.02,0:07:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and the theory that this\Nwas the origin of the Ol*mpics
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.44,0:07:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is today considered the most credible.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:15.61,0:07:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin, it's your turn!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a dangerous game... can you keep up?
Dialogue: 2,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The more dangerous the game,\Nthe more exciting it is.
Dialogue: 2,0:07:26.25,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you a man's game\Nthat will really make your crotch sting!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Instead of going\Nthrough the hoop, he ran past it!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:43.56,0:07:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh—this isn't good!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna hit your w**ner!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha—he actually did it!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 2,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? {\i1}Backspin{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:10.13,0:08:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right between the cheeks!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:13.42,0:08:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I'm always\Ntraining my sphincter muscle, huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:19.34,0:08:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have known: your w**ner\Nand your butt have airtight defenses!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:22.68,0:08:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Next up is Kanade. Your turn!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the right to\Nuse one of those anymore.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So you broke up with her?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd played a rock...!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, chin up.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:41.85,0:08:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are as many women as stars in the sky—
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.08,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what my big brother said.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We have some in our clinic, too. Wanna stop by?
Dialogue: 2,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gin, Tomu...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 2,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out—you're making us blush!
Dialogue: 2,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what friends are for!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.94,0:09:15.52,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– I {\i1}do{\i0} know this isn't what\NI meant by "waiting for Kanade"...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.68,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Should we get a teacher?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm curious about him.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.61,0:09:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kanade—
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Going home, Takahashi?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Tomu and Gin are in the\Nbathroom. I'm waiting for them.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:30.96,0:09:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade, I heard you\Nbroke up with your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:33.81,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, high-school girls are over the hill.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we're through.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:40.44,0:09:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what's taking them?\NOh, they might be pooping!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:44.53,0:09:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They {\i1}did{\i0} have seconds at lunch.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.32,0:09:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, yeah, being growing young men and all...
Dialogue: 2,0:09:49.62,0:09:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So am way, I'm a free agent now.
Dialogue: 2,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Then maybe I'll put in a bid!
Dialogue: 2,0:09:58.05,0:09:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, excuse me?
Dialogue: 2,0:09:59.93,0:10:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, what? Can't you see I'm bus—
Dialogue: 2,0:10:03.62,0:10:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what exactly are you doing here?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:06.58,0:10:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a deviant or anything, I just... um...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:11.41,0:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! I'm just a high-school girl\Ninterested in a primary-school boy!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.79,0:10:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You have got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just hearing things.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for waiting, figure skating!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:31.60,0:10:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You fed up? It's a setup!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:33.90,0:10:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye, Fukaya.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, gator!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:37.61,0:10:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment, if you please?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup!
Dialogue: 2,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry for the disturbance.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.37,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Kazu's muttler.
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.58,0:10:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutt? His pet?
Dialogue: 2,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Kazu's pet.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Such gracious words!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:03.76,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kanade, Master Tomu, Master Gin...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.55,0:11:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please lend me,\NMakurazaki Munemitsu, your assistance?
Dialogue: 2,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Kazu is in certain crisis!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.01,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The setup!
Comment: 2,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.25,0:11:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In the ten years since I began\Nmy service at the weaning ceremony
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.70,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,100 days after his birth,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:27.57,0:11:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I have never seen the\Nyoung master in such a state.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:35.54,0:11:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievably, that perfect young master...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:38.42,0:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...is confusing his Tuesday\Nand Wednesday schedules!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:42.14,0:11:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Failing to arrange his\Npencils by length in their case!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.36,0:11:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even misbuttoning his shirts!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:47.43,0:11:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kazu{\i0} is?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You could {\i1}probably{\i0} let that stuff slide...
Dialogue: 2,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be why. His temperature is 36{97}.2,
Dialogue: 2,0:11:54.98,0:11:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,so he is staying home from school.
Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.60,0:11:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kazu{\i0} is?!
Dialogue: 2,0:11:58.19,0:11:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a normal temperature.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:00.27,0:12:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It would appear that the young master
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.45,0:12:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,has been stricken with lovesickness!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:05.11,0:12:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.91,0:12:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, I beg of you!\NSeek out the object of his affection!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And when she is found...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:15.87,0:12:20.21,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– ...for the young master's sake,\NI, Makurazaki, will...!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.21,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Yikes!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.21,0:12:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on the case!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:26.82,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They see the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.80,0:12:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and look like adults but have the minds of kids!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Their name? The Bamboo\NPrimary Young Detective Squad!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:35.86,0:12:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, the Young\NDetective Squad is in business!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Jigen!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.79,0:12:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Goemon!
Dialogue: 2,0:12:44.19,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't those thieves, not detectives?
Dialogue: 2,0:12:47.62,0:12:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so according to our witness's testimony...
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A short while ago,
Dialogue: 2,0:12:52.09,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I fell in love with the\Nowner of this poem notebook.
Dialogue: 2,0:12:56.35,0:13:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Her tears and her pure heart poured\Nout in these pages touched me so...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.20,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Pure...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:02.95,0:13:04.25,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Poem?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:06.54,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No luck.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:07.95,0:13:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means Kasumi House\Nwasn't the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So where was this going on?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't happen in the gym!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:17.37,0:13:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the infirmary, either.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the bathrooms? We can't block those off!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:22.31,0:13:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... the police, not detectives.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:25.15,0:13:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A girl we've never met...
Dialogue: 2,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've solved the whole mystery!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandfather's name is Yonekichi!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:31.90,0:13:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:32.92,0:13:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit... is Bathroom Hanako!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:37.27,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I know I kind of got\Nswept up into following you here,
Dialogue: 2,0:13:40.70,0:13:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm going to head back.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:44.67,0:13:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Say what?!
Dialogue: 2,0:13:46.43,0:13:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako... is that her name?
Dialogue: 2,0:13:49.83,0:13:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. Our flawless deductions led us right to it.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:55.83,0:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So her name is Hanako.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.37,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And where does she live?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:05.83,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you this, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:07.99,0:14:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In the bathroom!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.65,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-In... the {\i1}bathroom{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:12.38,0:14:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Our search revealed that\Nshe's always in the bathroom.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:16.09,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way would a lady live somewhere like that!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:19.21,0:14:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's got a bad stomach.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:20.84,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah—so she's pooping.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.10,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rude thing to say about a lady!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:24.82,0:14:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Kazu. Even women get\Nupset stomachs sometimes.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:31.27,0:14:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means Hanako is suffering\Nalone in the bathroom even now...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,630)}Why don't you get some medicine to her?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,630)}I, the future OB/GYN, agree.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:45.29,0:14:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But to enter a bathroom with a lady present...
Dialogue: 2,0:14:49.08,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's far too early!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Kazu?
Dialogue: 2,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman you love is suffering!
Dialogue: 2,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't ignore that if it were me.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were me...!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:01.48,0:15:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade broke up with his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.58,0:15:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is that true, Kanade?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.80,0:15:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I—
Dialogue: 2,0:15:15.38,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not all over for you.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:18.65,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Get that medicine to the one you\Nlove with your own two hands!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:22.12,0:15:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanade... what a guy...!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:26.60,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, Kazu!
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.39,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See? We've got the medicine ready.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:31.80,0:15:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomu... Gin...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:40.95,0:15:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why all the snooping around... {\i1}Kouta{\i0}?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,More of your usual eavesdropping, eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Pure trash as ever.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:49.34,0:15:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! Kanade just came back really hyped up...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want to get involved.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're a nice toy for those brats.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a toy?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:04.21,0:16:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Young Detective Squad is on the move!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Detectives?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:11.05,0:16:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.38,0:16:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just between us...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:14.40,0:16:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...our sleuthwork has revealed\Nwho Kazu's mystery woman is.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:18.13,0:16:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazu? Oh, that normal primary-schooler.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:22.82,0:16:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it was love at first sight\Nwhen he saw her pure poems
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.88,0:16:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,at our place yesterday.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.39,0:16:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Love at first sight, eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:16:31.14,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Bathroom Hanako!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And if we can get the two of\Nthem together, it'll be case closed!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're off to the scene!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:42.72,0:16:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hang on a sec, Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:45.13,0:16:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:46.05,0:16:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard all about it.\NDon't be gettin' one up on me, now!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:50.64,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a job for Takahashi Jouji,\Nprimary-school detective of the west!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.47,0:16:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you joining us, Bro?!
Dialogue: 2,0:16:57.66,0:17:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The western Takahashi'll step\Nforth with the eastern Takahashi!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:01.93,0:17:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Takahashi all the way down!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, so... I'll just be going...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:11.08,0:17:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You know something about this.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:13.18,0:17:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:15.74,0:17:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what will happen\Nif you don't tell me... right?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... Kazu's mystery girl...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...is probably me, dressed as a girl.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:29.83,0:17:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.00,0:17:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You look like you just got a juicy scoop!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.68,0:17:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maaaybe.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Infiltration complete.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:40.34,0:17:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oof!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To the school building!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.97,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Roger!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.00,0:17:43.97,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Yep!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodger!
Dialogue: 2,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,For the class president\Nto be doing such a thing...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.12,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No—not as long as it's for her.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I get dragged into this?
Dialogue: 2,0:17:56.47,0:17:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Children need supervision, right? Come on.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako's poem notebook.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:11.29,0:18:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd return it\Nthe next time I saw her...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.69,0:18:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I've kept it on me.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:16.55,0:18:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... You know, she might\Njust be a lot closer than you think.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:22.50,0:18:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I never thought\Nwe'd be at the same school.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:28.04,0:18:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's locked!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} night...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:32.26,0:18:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that makes this a locked room?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not a room.
Dialogue: 2,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.35,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Anybody there?!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.35,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Kanade!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:40.82,0:18:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A locked room? That's the perfect crime!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:42.94,0:18:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The primary-school detective\Nof the west'll solve this for sure!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:47.23,0:18:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Bro!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.91,0:18:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We might have been way wrong about all this!
Dialogue: 2,0:18:52.59,0:18:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha mean, Kanade?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:54.31,0:18:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How could Hanako have gotten\Ninto the school if it's locked?
Dialogue: 2,0:18:59.48,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right... Teachers should be\Nthe only ones with keys to the school.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:03.92,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on: then Hanako\Ncan't get into the bathroom!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:07.68,0:19:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this conversation taking a strange turn?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:10.71,0:19:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's the harm?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.02,0:19:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Hanako could get in {\i1}without{\i0} a key.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.22,0:19:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Kanade... if that's true, then...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako's really a...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:21.91,0:19:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's too unscientific to be true!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you know?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:29.32,0:19:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Bathroom Hanako...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.98,0:19:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...is a ghost.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Q?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.25,0:19:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Atsushi, are you serious?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, oh no, oh no!
Dialogue: 2,0:19:37.60,0:19:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I just remembered something I have to do.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.19,0:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Gin is {\i1}not{\i0} running away.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:41.19,0:19:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I spotted the entrance to the\Ncontinent of Mu over there is all.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.23,0:19:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Y'all are a buncha babies\Nif y'all are scared of a li'l ghost...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:46.87,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako's a ghost?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:48.43,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm betting the girl you\Nlike is {\i1}not{\i0} Bathroom Hanako.
Dialogue: 2,0:19:55.80,0:19:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Guys?
Dialogue: 2,0:19:57.39,0:19:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, they left!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:00.44,0:20:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids are the best.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were going to tell them she was a ghost,
Dialogue: 2,0:20:04.26,0:20:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you should have told them right away!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:06.91,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:09.43,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You handle this, you stupid spook!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:11.81,0:20:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Wait up!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:14.14,0:20:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Stop right there!
Dialogue: 2,0:20:23.43,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanako...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't be having this, you know.
Dialogue: 2,0:20:31.91,0:20:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Pulling this nonsense twice in one day?
Dialogue: 2,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what made me db it!
Comment: 2,0:22:07.61,0:22:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 2,0:22:09.61,0:22:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Poop!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.82,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Poop!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:10.98,0:22:12.82,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– Poop!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:12.82,0:22:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so excited to be\Ntalking about p—er, number two?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:19.45,0:22:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, it seems there were once\Nmany children who couldn't p—
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.90,0:22:28.25,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– ...go number two in the school bathrooms.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:25.83,0:22:28.25,Default,alt,0,0,0,,– My turn at last! Phew!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:29.25,0:22:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were like that when we were kids.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:33.13,0:22:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi! It's the other way around!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your spoken line and\Nyour inner monologue are switched!
Dialogue: 2,0:22:38.39,0:22:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Found out, eh?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure was rough back then.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:43.20,0:22:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once they found out\Nyou did number two at school,
Dialogue: 2,0:22:45.64,0:22:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd get stuck with the\Nnickname "Pooperman" till graduation.
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.36,0:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you do when you had to poop?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:53.48,0:22:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Just hold it till you get home... maybe?
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.90,0:22:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you {\i1}couldn't{\i0}?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:01.78,0:23:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If ya don't wanna get caught,\Ndo it before anyone sees ya.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:05.79,0:23:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Naniwa Speed Coaster\Nis a speedy pooper, too!
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.33,0:23:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But why hide it? Everyone poops, right?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:14.18,0:23:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen. Heck, I always tell\Nthe girls before I'm off to poop.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.80,0:23:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Gin, show some restraint.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:22.39,0:23:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it really was rough.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:25.00,0:23:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't go to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:26.93,0:23:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.89,0:23:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:29.21,0:23:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:30.40,0:23:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Taga?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:31.44,0:23:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}don't{\i0}.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:33.44,0:23:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you an idol?
Dialogue: 2,0:23:35.23,0:23:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka Ken here.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming up on First Love Monster...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:39.28,0:23:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanaka. Ken. Tanaka Ken here.
Dialogue: 2,0:23:43.83,0:23:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All on the next First Love Monster:
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.70,0:23:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,"Kanade's Telephone Helpline."
